Introduction

Suzy is a South Korean singer and actress currently under Management SOOP. She is best known for being a member of the girl group miss A.

In 2009, Suzy auditioned for Mnet Superstar K and made it through the preliminary round but she was eliminated. However, she caught the attention of a scout from JYP Entertainment and soon became a trainee. She made her official debut in July of 2010 with girl group miss A.

In 2017, Suzy made her solo debut with album titled "Yes? No?". On December 27th 2017 JYP Entertainment announced that Miss A had disbanded and Suzy had renewed her contract with JYP Entertainment.

On March 31st, 2019, Suzy announced she would not be renewing her contract with JYP Entertainment following the expiration. She signed with SOOP Management.
